BioMart,provides,free,software,and,data,services,to,the,international,scientific,community,in,order,to,foster,scientific,collaboration,and,facilitate,the,scientific,discovery,process,A,number,of,servers,providing,access,to,a,wide,range,of,research,data,have,been,set,up,by,the,BioMart,community,Using,BioMart,s,data,federation,technology,Data,Portals,have,been,established,to,provide,a,convenient,single,point,of,access,to,all,of,these,data,servers